00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,000
Only the most elegant food

294
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
can be compared with your temperament.

295
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,000
Sister.

296
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,000
Why are there still

297
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,000
so many customers' dishes?

298
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,000
Go, go, go.

299
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,000
Brother Chun went out to pick up the dishes.

300
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,000
Be careful of customers complaining about you.

301
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,000
Boss Meng won't buy you sugar.

302
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,000
I know, I know.

303
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,000
You're taking money to help people.

304
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,000
Tong Feng.

305
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,000
This is Si Mo who just came.

306
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,000
He will try Wangchuan Soup Shop from now on.

307
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,000
Hello, Si Mo.

308
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,000
Okay, Tong Feng.

309
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,000
This class ends here.

310
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,000
The grass in Wangchuan Soup Shop is almost gone.

311
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,000
I have to go to the grass in Yuancang Mountain.

312
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,000
I can only come back in a few days.

313
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,000
You're leaving now?

314
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,000
You're in such a hurry.

315
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
If it weren't for the class,

316
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:36,000
I would have left a long time ago.

317
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,000
Since you're busy,

318
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,000
I'll stay and help.

319
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,000
Okay.

320
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
I'm leaving then.

