00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,000
Thank you.

326
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,000
I also think I'm pretty.

327
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,000
I like you.

328
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,000
Thank you.

329
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,000
I also like myself.

330
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:19,000
Do you really know what I'm doing?

331
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:23,000
Or are you playing hard to get?

332
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,000
I know.

333
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,000
I won't let you...

334
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,000
Be careful.

335
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,000
It's hot.

336
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,000
It's not cooked yet.

337
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,000
Xuankai.

338
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:46,000
You're so pretty.

339
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,000
What are you talking about?

340
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,000
Xuankai.

341
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:51,000
I really like you.

342
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:56,000
What are you talking about?

343
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
Xuankai.

344
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:10,000
Let me taste the osmanthus cake, okay?

345
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,000
Xuankai.

346
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,000
Why are you so hot?

347
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,000
It's...

348
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,000
It's a little hot.

349
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
It's...

350
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,000
Hot?

351
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,000
You want to eat a cake?

352
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:33,000
Ma Yi Chuan came to me today

353
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:35,000
and tricked me into eating the candy in my pocket.

354
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,000
And a new friend

355
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
used the same method

356
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,000
and took the candy you gave me.

357
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,000
I want to use this method

358
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,000
to trick Xuankai

359
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,000
into giving me the osmanthus cake.

360
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,000
Wangchuan Cuisine

361
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,000
is very thoughtful.

362
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,000
Remember to give me a gift.

363
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,000
Xiao Mengzi is not here.

364
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,000
Who gave this to you?

365
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,000
I'm sorry.

366
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:23,000
So this is from Si Mo.

367
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,000
Xuankai.

368
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,000
Who is Si Mo?

369
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,000
Si Mo is

370
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,000
a pretty young man

371
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,000
that Xiao Mengzi hired.

372
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,000
He is the friend you just met?

373
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,000
So he is the one who asked you

374
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,000
for the candy?

375
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,000
Yes.

376
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,000
You ate his cake.

377
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,000
Don't eat mine.

378
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,000
Xuankai.

379
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:58,000
Are you angry?

