00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,000
No.

381
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:04,000
No?

382
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,000
No.

383
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,000
In the future,

384
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:14,000
when you are angry with the adults,

385
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,000
you can use the practice of calligraphy to coax him.

386
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,000
No matter how angry he is,

387
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,000
he will be angry instantly.

388
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:37,000
I dream of you even if I'm lost.

389
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:40,000
In the misty rain,

390
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:43,000
the light is bright.

391
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:50,000
My heart will forever shine for you.

392
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:55,000
Oh.

393
00:18:55,000 --> 00:19:00,000
In the misty rain,

394
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:02,000
the light is bright.

395
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:07,000
Oh.

396
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:09,000
In the night,

397
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:14,000
I look forward to the spring.

398
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:19,000
It is hard to say goodbye.

399
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:22,000
Fate is uncertain.

400
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:28,000
How can I exchange my thoughts?

401
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:31,000
The sound of the flute is echoing.

402
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:34,000
The fireworks are shining.

403
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:41,000
I am looking forward to it.

